title: Logano spins out Kenseth late, wins at Kansas Speedway (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,361 Logano spins out Kenseth late, wins at Kansas Speedway (Yahoo Sports) Joey Logano could have backed off. Logano ultimately drove away for his second straight win in the Chase for the Sprint Cup championship, while Kenseth was left in a win-or-else situation heading into next weekend's race at Talladega. ''I'm really disappointed,'' Kenseth said.
